# Usage

### Feature extraction

```bash
cd /path/to/qc_final

mkdir output
python3 ./code/feature_extraction.py \
-i ./test_data/single_fast5 \
-o ./output \
-t 3 --group RawGenomeCorrected_000
```



### Read-level probability prediction

```bash
python3 ./code/predict_mod_probs.py \
-i ./output/tmp \
-o ./output/probs.csv \
--device cuda:0 \
--model ./models/biLSTM_model \
--scaler ./models/scaler
```



### Stoichiometry estimation

```bash
python3 ./code/mod_rate_calibration.py \
-i ./output/probs.csv \
-o ./output/mod_rate.csv \
--device cuda:0 \
--model ./models/regression_model
```

